name: SMOKE
description:
SMOKE !!!
Part of depression art !!!
.
Smoking is primarily practiced as a route of administration for recreational drug use because the combustion of the dried plant leaves vaporizes and delivers active substances into the lungs where they are rapidly absorbed into the bloodstream and reach bodily tissue. And for that purpose, sometime smoker ignore his/her own health, even his/her closest person to him/her. Because we all know that smoking is not only bad for the smoker, but also bad for the other.
